    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 single-condition test as a worst-case loading scenario. All three QoIs satisfy both the 10% difference bound and the E/uval < 1.96 threshold. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level conclusion for this COU.",
